1 ATTRIBUTABLE TO THE PROGRAM, INCLUDING PERSONNEL HIRED BY THE OFFICE
2 AND ASSIGNED TO THE PROGRAM.
3 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
4 October 1, 2025. It shall remain effective for a period of 3 years and, at the end of September
5 30, 2028, this Act, with no further action required by the General Assembly, shall be
6 abrogated and of no further force and effect.

